==Japanese==
[[Category:Japanese language|ぎんのだんがん]]

===Etymology===
A literal translation of ''silver bullet'', [[銀]]の ''of [[silver]]'' + [[弾丸]] ''[[bullet]]''.

===Noun phrase===
'''銀の弾丸''' (ぎんのだんがん, gin no dangan)

#A straightforward solution perceived to have extreme effectiveness or miraculous results; [[silver bullet]].